其中需要12個五角星和20個三個菱形的組合<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://americanhistory.si.edu/collections/search/object/nmah_1066685 | title = Geometric Model by Dick Holl, a Student of A.Harry Wheeler, Dodecadodecahedron | publisher = americanhistory.si.edu | access-date = 2019-09-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190926153741/https://americanhistory.si.edu/collections/search/object/nmah_1066685 | archive-date = 2019-09-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。由於這種結構使用了5個菱形來代替原有星形多面體的正五邊形面，因此組合出來的形狀部會包含原本就隱沒於截半大十二面體中的部分。<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.polyhedra.net/en/model.php?name-en=dodecadodecahedron | title = Paper Dodecadodecahedron | publisher = polyhedra.net}}</ref>在這種結構下的截半大十二面體共由12個五角星面和60個菱形組成，且具有72個面、120條邊和90個頂點<ref>{{cite web | url = https://polyhedr.com/dodecadodecahedron2.html | title = Dodecadodecahedron | publisher = polyhedr.com | access-date = 2019-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190926161202/https://polyhedr.com/dodecadodecahedron2.html | archive-date = 2019-09-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

