=== 拓樸正多面體 ===
由於截半大十二面體的五角星形面可經由拓樸變形變為五邊形面，因此，這種形狀在拓樸中相當於[[四階五邊形鑲嵌|四階五邊形鑲嵌]]的商空間。<ref name="David A. Richter 2005">{{Cite web | url = http://homepages.wmich.edu/~drichter/golay.htm | title = The Dodecadodecahedron and the Golay Code | publisher = wmich.edu | author = David A. Richter | access-date = 2013-05-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181018051918/http://homepages.wmich.edu/~drichter/golay.htm | archive-date = 2018-10-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{citation|first=H. S. M.|last=Coxeter|authorlink=H. S. M. Coxeter|series=The Beauty of Geometry: Twelve Essays|year=1999|publisher=Dover Publications|lccn=99035678|isbn=0-486-40919-8|title=Chapter 10: Regular honeycombs in hyperbolic space|url=http://www.mathunion.org/ICM/ICM1954.3/Main/icm1954.3.0155.0169.ocr.pdf|access-date=2019-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610043106/http://www.mathunion.org/ICM/ICM1954.3/Main/icm1954.3.0155.0169.ocr.pdf|archive-date=2016-06-10|dead-url=no}}, invited lecture, ICM, Amsterdam, 1954.</ref>下圖中的紅色與黃色的五邊形分別代表拓樸形變前的五角星和正五邊形。
