此外，截半大十二面體也是一種不存在良好具像化實例的抽象正多面體的部分具像化實例之一<ref>[http://homepages.wmich.edu/~drichter/regularpolyhedra.htm The Regular Polyhedra (of index two)] {{Wayback|url=http://homepages.wmich.edu/~drichter/regularpolyhedra.htm |date=20160304023021 }}, David A. Richter</ref><ref>[http://homepages.wmich.edu/~drichter/golay.htm The Golay Code on the Dodecadodecahedron] {{Wayback|url=http://homepages.wmich.edu/~drichter/golay.htm |date=20181018051918 }}, David A. Richter</ref>。在考克斯特於1977年出版的著作《{{link-en|正多胞形 (書籍)|Regular_Polytopes_(book)|正多胞形}}》中列出了五種不存在良好具像化實例的抽象正多面體。後來在1987年{{link-de|耶爾格·邁克爾·威利|Jörg Michael Wills}}的論文又再次的確定了共存在五種有這種性質的抽象正多面體。<ref name="article wills1987combinatorially">{{cite journal
  |title=The combinatorially regular polyhedra of index 2
  |author=Wills, Jörg Michael
  |journal=aequationes mathematicae
  |volume=34
  |number=2-3
  |pages=206--220
  |year=1987
  |publisher=Springer}}</ref>這種抽象多面體具有C<sub>2</sub>×S<sub>5</sub>對稱性，但只能具像化出一半的對稱性，即C<sub>2</sub>×A<sub>5</sub>或二十面體群對稱性。<ref name="David A. Richter">{{Cite web | url = http://homepages.wmich.edu/~drichter/regularpolyhedra.htm | title = The Regular Polyhedra (of index two) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304023021/http://homepages.wmich.edu/~drichter/regularpolyhedra.htm | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | author = David A. Richter | publisher = [[西密西根大學|西密西根大學]]}}</ref><ref name="arxiv:1005.4911">[https://arxiv.org/pdf/1005.4911.pdf Regular Polyhedra of Index Two, I] {{Wayback|url=https://arxiv.org/pdf/1005.4911.pdf |date=20180828102425 }} Anthony M. Cutler, Egon Schulte, 2010</ref><ref name="Beitrage zur Algebra und Geometrie">[https://www.researchgate.net/publication/225386108_Regular_Polyhedra_of_Index_Two_II Regular Polyhedra of Index Two, II] {{Wayback|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/225386108_Regular_Polyhedra_of_Index_Two_II |date=20180828134402 }}  Beitrage zur Algebra und Geometrie 52(2):357–387 · November 2010, Table 3, p.27</ref>

截半大十二面體在拓樸學上由24個五邊形組成，且每個頂點都是4個五邊形的公共頂點，因此在拓樸學上滿足抽象正多面體的定義。<ref name="David A. Richter"/><ref name="arxiv:1005.4911"/><ref name="Beitrage zur Algebra und Geometrie"/>然而這種抽象面體若是具象化為截半大十二面體則僅能具象化一半的對稱性。這種抽象正多面體可以對應到虧格為4的四階五邊形正則地區圖（施萊夫利符號：{5,4}<sub>6</sub>）<ref name= "Regular Map S4:{5,4}" >{{cite web | url = http://www.weddslist.com/rmdb/map.php?a=R4.2p | title = S4:{5,4} | publisher = Regular Map database - map details, weddslist.com | accessdate = 2021-10-16 }}</ref>，對應的皮特里多邊形為六邊形<ref name= "Regular Map S4:{5,4}"/>。

